bib_record.title: Results of time-of-flight transmission measurements for 103Rh at a 50 m station of GELINA

free_txt: Cin:  TOF spectrum of sample-in measurement
Bin:  TOF spectrum of sample-in background
Cout: TOF spectrum of sample-out measurement
Bout: TOF spectrum of sample-out background
K:    Systematic effect due to background model
- Two water filled Be-containers around U target
2x(14.6 cm x 21 cm x 3.9 cm) at the room temperature
as moderators placed above and below U target.
- Flight path direction w.r.t. normal of the
moderator face viewing the flight path  = 9 deg
- Diameter of neutron beam at sample position = 45 mm
- Overlap suppression filter: 1.5 mm Cd overlap filter
- Other neutron beam filters: Na, Co, Ag, W, Pb
